snippet.textDisplay:
I can't believe that I've found this song only now. I'm feeling such a strong sense of loss, loss of the time I could've listened to it, passionately gushed about it to friends, daydreaming to this song, getting lost in my own world listening to this song while being surrounded by a crowd. 
Vaibhav Modi you are fantastic...Papon you've brought his (and of so many others) feelings to life. Every artist related to this song and the video, so amazing.
